OOC: are all of the Terrorcons here? Also, Jer, reply to 
Switchblade. =)

--- Astroblast / Dead-End / Drag Strip / Rippersnapper ---

Astroblast frowns, initially ignoring Breakdown, "Hun-Grr, get your 
Terrocons over here, now." He thinks about what to do, then turns 
to Stratus as he notices the other bot's arrival. "Stratus, we are 
heading to these coordinates," he gives Stratus the exact 
coordinates, "with the crashed ship in the water. I need you to 
scout a path so as to avoid enemy activity. Go." He finishes giving 
Stratus orders, and turns to the Stunticons, "Well Breakdown, 
since the ship's underwater, I think you know the answer to that." 
He shakes his head and continues, "Motormaster, form Menasor. 
When all of the Terrorcons are here, we'll have Abominus speed up 
the process." He thinks to himself, <welll, hopefully the stupid bot 
will follow orders without too much trouble...>

Dead-End and Drag Strip nod, and look to Motormaster for the 
transformation cue.

Turning to Cyclonus, he gives the ariel bot some orders, 
"Cyclonus, you are going to patrol the airways while we move the 
ship. If you see any disturbances report immediately so that we 
may take care of them. Oh, and don't get out of our sight, we need 
to have backup if any enemy targets show up to try to stop our 
progress." His curt nod indicates that he is finished with Cyclonus, 
and he looks at the other bots present.

Rippersnapper thinks hard to himself, and for once (maybe twice) 
in his life, he said something that made sense, "Sinnertwin, You 
screw up, Megatron not be happy." He waits impatiently for other 
Terrorcons to arrive so that they may form Abominus.
